<p>Welcome to Bangla Web Fonts (<a href="https://banglawebfonts.pages.dev">https://banglawebfonts.pages.dev</a>). This Cookie Policy explains how we use cookies, caching, and similar technologies on our website.</p>

    <h2>1. What Are Cookies?</h2>
    <p>Cookies are small text files stored on your device when you visit a website. They help improve your experience by remembering preferences and analyzing traffic.</p>

    <h2>2. How We Use Cookies</h2>
    <p>We use cookies for the following purposes:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Performance and Security:</strong> Cloudflare uses cookies to enhance website security and optimize load times.</li>
        <li><strong>Analytics:</strong> Cloudflare Analytics may set cookies to collect anonymous data about website traffic and usage patterns.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>3. Third-Party Cookies</h2>
    <p>We use Cloudflare services, which may set cookies as part of their security and analytics features. You can read Cloudflare’s privacy policy <a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/privacypolicy/" target="_blank">here</a>.</p>

    <h2>4. Service Worker and Offline Storage</h2>
    <p>Our website uses a service worker to enable offline functionality as part of a Progressive Web App (PWA). This service worker:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Caches website content on your browser to improve performance and allow offline access.</li>
        <li>Does not collect or send any personal data to our servers.</li>
        <li>Only stores data locally on your device, which you can clear at any time through your browser settings.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>5. Managing Cookies and Storage</h2>
    <p>You can manage or disable cookies through your browser settings. You can also clear cached data stored by the service worker at any time by clearing your browser’s storage and cache.</p>

    <h2>6. Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>We may update this Cookie Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page.</p>

    <h2>7. Contact Us</h2>
    <p>If you have any questions, please contact us at <a href="https://banglawebfonts.pages.dev/contact">our contact page</a>.</p>


